dct_description_sm: Ancillary maps: The vicinity of Sozhou -- Huqui Hill (Tiger Hill) -- Zhouzheng (Humble Administrator's Garden) --Liuyuan Garden (Remaining Garden) -- Shizilin (Llion Grove Garden) Selected buildings shown pictorially. Business District located. Tourist information on verso.
